on high;
Come unto Jesus, for why will ye die?
3 Come, discontented, in debt and
distressed;
Come, is the Saviour's most urgent
request;
"Come, everyone," is His worldwide
call;
Come, for "all things are now ready"
for all.
4 Jesus has power on earth to forgive,
Jesus has power to make dead sinners
live;
Jesus will never cast out those who
come;
